<br>
3. put a limit of 2 people per guild on the list at the same time.  if you left a guild that has 2 people on the list now within the last 2 months, you count as being in that guild.  this rule will make the list shorter.  the list being shorter will mean that your 3rd person gets onto it more quickly.<br>
<br>
